subject: Golf
Greenbrier Classic (Golf)
lead_paragraph: Tommy Gainey and Johnson Wagner each shot an eight-under-par 62 to share a two-stroke lead after the first round of the Greenbrier Classic in White Sulphur Springs, W.Va.
